=Episode 23=

4
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,359
Gu Zhiqian's paintings

5
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:49,000
are full of liveliness and energy.

6
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:52,200
He must have been someone
who roamed freely

7
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,519
among mountains and rivers.

8
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:57,239
I don't know why he became
like this now.

9
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,680
Then I also ask you,

10
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,439
I am also lively and energetic.

11
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,680
If this continues,

12
00:02:03,159 --> 00:02:04,879
I'll end up just like him.

13
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,879
If you don't want to study,

14
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,360
then go to sleep quickly.

15
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:10,120
I need to close the window,

16
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,599
so he won't notice.

17
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,800
It's strange.

18
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:21,680
What is it?

19
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:22,840
He…

20
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,039
The light in his study is out.

21
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:27,919
It was on just now.

22
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,560
Didn't he say
he'd study through the night?

23
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:43,439
Brother, this painting is excellent.

24
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,680
Truly excellent.

25
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:45,919
Wait...

26
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:46,680
Brother?

27
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,439
What does this painting

28
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,080
still lack?

29
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,879
Who is he talking to?

30
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,479
Autumn has deepened,

31
00:03:00,159 --> 00:03:01,800
the mountains lie desolate.

32
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,560
It feels truly cold and lonely.

33
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:05,960
This hint of human presence here

34
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,599
is perfect.

35
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,439
Perfect, indeed.

36
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,159
Did you see that?

37
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,840
That painting is moving.

38
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,759
"My master has gone to gather herbs,

39
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:17,520
somewhere within these mountains.

40
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:20,479
The clouds are too thick
to see through."

41
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,240
In that case,

42
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:32,039
then I'll paint the man who asks the boy
for directions under the pines.

43
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,080
Brother, are you a hermit?

44
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,400
To me,

45
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,719
you are like an apothecary
hidden in the mountains.

46
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,599
Though we are separated

47
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,800
by life and death,

48
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:07,080
my heart still yearns for you.

49
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:16,199
"The Five Peaks stand
at the heart of heaven and earth.

50
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,720
I hear that you remain,

51
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,120
still upon the highest summit."

52
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,279
Brother, that ease of spirit

53
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:28,040
is something I, Gu Zhiqian,

54
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:30,879
will never master in this lifetime.

55
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:33,160
What's going on here?

56
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:36,279
Is someone painting together with him?

57
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,519
Could it be…

58
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,079
Zhao Wanli.

59
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:47,460
(Youlan Alley)

60
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,279
Serves you right.

61
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,759
I told you not to mess
with that hole on the roof.

62
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,480
You just wouldn't listen.

63
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,519
Clumsy as ever.

64
00:04:58,519 --> 00:05:00,290
Do you think
you're some sky-leaping monkey?

65
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:05,360
I've got it.

66
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,600
I've got it.

67
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:08,000
Got what?

68
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,639
Look.

69
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,680
The storm over Jiang City has passed,

70
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:14,319
by dusk, brush and ink turn cool.

71
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:16,560
Gu just wrote this.

72
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,199
Who's Gu?

73
