I've waited over half a month for him.

74
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,560
It nearly drove me mad.

75
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,160
I need to head back.

76
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,839
I need to answer this.

77
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:30,639
Watch where you're going.

78
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:50,639
The storm over Jiang City has passed,

79
00:05:52,319 --> 00:05:54,439
by dusk, brush and ink turn cool.

80
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:58,399
The storm over Jiang City has passed,

81
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:02,360
by dusk, brush and ink turn cool.

82
00:06:11,890 --> 00:06:13,990
Though my hair is white,
my spirit is still strong,

83
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,920
my ambition for the clouds
